      "comment": "DON'T LOOK (2) lines up chasing another win after getting around the 390m at this track in a strong 22.24 on May 7. In winning form and can measure up again. GOT A FORMULA (8) hit the frame on debut then from the inside draw got off the mark, scoring by 2.5 lengths at Wagga over 320m (18.41). Shows good ability and expected to feature. SAINT HARVEY (1) led throughout to score two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 9 length 6th at this track (22.93). Strong form has emerged from his last run. Can do much better this time. STAR BLUEY (3) scored in dominant fashion last time. Big chance on that form.",
